695
00:47:47.700 --> 00:47:50.600
Some man gave it to me, saying it's for unit 401.

696
00:47:50.600 --> 00:47:51.709
I see.

697
00:47:53.109 --> 00:47:55.580
(I'm leaving the bag here as you told me not to call you. Yong Suk.)

