707
00:48:48.399 --> 00:48:51.330
Hey, you know my mom makes so much food every time.

708
00:48:52.470 --> 00:48:54.669
Do you want to go out since it's the weekend?

709
00:48:55.100 --> 00:48:56.269
Soo Ji.

710
00:48:57.740 --> 00:49:01.339
I'm going to Namhae today.

711
00:49:01.339 --> 00:49:04.410
