744
00:51:41.999 --> 00:51:44.839
do recycling, and clean up after my cat's poop.

745
00:51:44.839 --> 00:51:46.140
That's what I told her.

746
00:51:46.410 --> 00:51:48.309
- Is that wrong? - What do you mean by that?

747
00:51:48.379 --> 00:51:50.839
I mean, even if you don't like her,

748
00:51:51.010 --> 00:51:54.350
